      "oddsUpdateTime": "0001-01-01T01:00:00.000Z",
      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"3. LUCY MCGEE resumes from a spell of seven months. Could only manage to finish sixth at the latest run over 1308m at Kentucky (Turf). Good effort to kick-off last prep when in the money at Churchill Downs Turf over 1006m. Has ability and sure to prove tough to beat. 5. AURORA SKY returns after ten weeks in the paddock. Closed the last campaign with a fourth over 1106m at Fairgrounds Turf (Turf). Bold showing expected. 8. HEADSPIN did a fair job on debut last time out, finishing 1.4 lengths from the winner in fourth over 1006m at Gulfstream Park All Weather (Synthetic). One of the main contenders. 2. GELLHORN returned from a spell seven-and-a-half weeks ago when she was in contention on the corner before being beaten 2.75 lengths into fourth over 1609m at Gulfstream Park Turf. Likely improver with top-three prospects.\",\"runners\":[3,5,8,2],\"exclusive\":false}",
